      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled garage since its initial purchase. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin retains its factory-fresh aroma; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of creasing or wear, and the side bolsters remain as firm as the day it rolled off the assembly line. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the ambient lighting and seat heaters, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been maintained exclusively by certified master technicians, with a complete, documented service history binder included in the sale. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage reflects the car\u2019s limited exposure to the elements. This is a collector-grade investment for the discerning driver who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
